data.description: UPDATE:  Seller willing to pay buyers closing costs!!!  Check out this cozy traditional 3 Bed 2 full and 2 half bath home, nestled between the popular Bates Hendricks and Garfield Park.  Older home with updated feel, well taken care of by the current owner, new triple pane sound reduction windows, wonderful back yard to entertain, off street parking.  This is the perfect home for entertaining, all the rooms are large and spacious and you have such a nice back yard for BBQ's. Garfield Park is directly across the street enjoy walks for yourself or your pet, 5 minutes to Fountain Square for entertainment and dining, easy access to the interstate and a 5 minute drive to downtown Indy.
